value.package.json:
{
  "name": "data-analysis-demo",
  "version": "2.25.251",
  "description": "Client-side build system for Data Analysis Demo Web Application",
  "main": "index.js",
  "scripts": {
    "install-deps": "npm install",
    "build": "npm run clean && npm run bundle",
    "build-dev": "npm run clean && npm run bundle-dev",
    "clean": "rimraf dawpm/site.js dawpm/site.min.js dawpm/site.css dawpm/site.min.css",
    "bundle": "webpack --mode=production",
    "bundle-dev": "webpack --mode=development",
    "watch": "webpack --mode=development --watch",
    "serve": "webpack serve --mode=development"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "css-loader": "^7.1.2",
    "css-minimizer-webpack-plugin": "^7.0.2",
    "mini-css-extract-plugin": "^2.9.4",
    "rimraf": "^6.1.2",
    "style-loader": "^4.0.0",
    "terser-webpack-plugin": "^5.3.14",
    "webpack": "^5.103.0",
    "webpack-cli": "^6.0.1",
    "webpack-dev-server": "^5.2.2"
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "bootstrap": "^5.3.8",
    "c3": "^0.7.20",
    "chosen-js": "^1.8.7",
    "d3": "^7.9.0",
    "datatables.net": "^2.3.5",
    "datatables.net-bs5": "^2.3.5",
    "datatables.net-fixedheader-bs5": "^4.0.5",
    "datatables.net-responsive-bs5": "^3.0.7",
    "datatables.net-scroller-bs5": "^2.4.3",
    "datatables.net-searchpanes-bs5": "^2.3.5",
    "datatables.net-select-bs5": "^3.1.3",
    "jquery": "^3.7.1",
    "jquery-csv": "^1.0.40",
    "jquery-ui": "^1.14.1",
    "slick-carousel": "^1.8.1"
  },
  "author": "Mark Hazleton",
  "license": "MIT",
  "repository": {
    "type": "git",
    "url": "https://github.com/markhazleton/DataAnalysisDemo.git"
  }
}
